process information.

26
00:01:04.405 --> 00:01:08.155
For example, take The
Cafe Wall Illusion.

27
00:01:08.155 --> 00:01:11.310
In this image, the lines are
all horizontal and vertical,

28
00:01:11.310 --> 00:01:13.615
but part of our visual
processing system

29
00:01:13.615 --> 00:01:15.715
