44
00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:52.155
We can do this by asking
three simple questions;

45
00:01:52.155 --> 00:01:54.135
Why am I creating this chart?

46
00:01:54.135 --> 00:01:57.215
Who is it for? What does
it need to tell them?

47
00:01:57.215 --> 00:01:59.570
The answers to these
questions should

48
00:01:59.570 --> 00:02:01.690
